  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Optovue has implemented a motion contrast imaging software in RTVue XR, a split spectrum
      amplitude decorrelation algorithm (SSADA), for non-invasive imaging of ocular vasculature.
      Consented subjects will undergo a series of images of the back of the eye using an Optical
      Coherence Tomograpy (OCT) device, RTVue XR, in addition to the conventional images as part of
      clinical routine. SSADA images will be compared with conventional methods.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
